https://github.com/ondra-h/CzechStemmerDictionary).

You may either use the tools from command line (see Main class),
or as a library in your own application. The Main class may be 
a good starting point to learn how to use the library.


DISCLAIMER:

This work is highly experimental, most of it is intended just as a proof-of-concept. 
There are certainly bugs I don't know of and some of them might be serious (infinite 
loops, unchecked input etc.)
 
IT IS NOT RECOMMENDED TO DEPLOY AND USE THE SOFTWARE IN A PRODUCTION ENVIRONMENT. 
